    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "Quandary of Solstice",
        "Description": "The longest day of the year. The sun has still not set in Sapienza.\rYet despite the lovely weather, we have a dilemma.\r\rWe tracked the mysterious eco-mogul, Mr. Green, to this location. We believe he is here to meet with a disgraced quantum physicist specialising in solar energy. Our client has concerns about the direction of the company given the scientist&apos;s association with Ether. It would be rash to engage directly at this stage. Eliminate Mr. Green&apos;s entourage and we will follow as he flees.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as magicdave94.",
